To compile and run MicroC from within the docker image,

cd microc
docker run --rm -it -v `pwd`:/home/microc -w=/home/microc columbiasedwards/plt
make

docker build -t columbiasedwards/plt .

docker login -u columbiasedwards -p <password>

docker tag columbiasedwards/plt:latest columbiasedwards/plt

docker push columbiasedwards/plt